"The following items impact the comparability and presentation of our consolidated data:", "bbox": [56.3, 994.0, 798.5, 1014.7]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [131.3, 1034.5, 138.6, 1055.2]}, {"text": "In 2012 we acquired Ideas International, Inc. and recognized $2.4 million in pre-tax acquisition and integration", "bbox": [206.3, 1034.5, 1187.0, 1055.2]}, {"text": "charges (see Note 2 — Acquisitions in the Notes to the Consolidated Financial Statements). In addition, in 2009 we", "bbox": [206.3, 1058.5, 1187.0, 1079.3]}, {"text": "acquired AMR Research, Inc. and Burton Group, Inc., and in 2010 and 2009 we recognized $7.9 million and $2.9", "bbox": [206.3, 1082.3, 1186.9, 1103.0]}, {"text": "million in pre-tax acquisition charges. The results of these businesses, which were not material, were included", "bbox": [206.3, 1106.3, 1186.8, 1127.0]}, {"text": "beginning on their respective acquisition dates.", "bbox": [206.3, 1130.3, 598.7, 1151.0]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [131.3, 1171.1, 138.5, 1191.8]}, {"text": "In 2012 we repurchased 2.7 million of our common shares under our share repurchase program at a total cost of", "bbox": [206.3, 1171.1, 1186.7, 1191.8]}, {"text": "$111.3 million. We also repurchased 5.9 million, 3.9 million, 0.3 million, and 9.7 million of our common shares in", "bbox": [206.3, 1194.8, 1186.9, 1215.6]}, {"text": "2011, 2010, 2009, and 2008, respectively (see Note 7 — Stockholders’ Equity in the Notes to the Consolidated", "bbox": [206.3, 1218.8, 1186.9, 1239.6]}, {"text": "Financial Statements).", "bbox": [206.3, 1242.8, 392.6, 1263.6]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [131.3, 1283.6, 138.5, 1304.4]}, {"text": "In 2010 we refinanced our debt (see Note 5 — Debt in the Notes to the Consolidated Financial Statements). In", "bbox": [206.3, 1283.6, 1187.1, 1304.4]}, {"text": "conjunction with the refinancing, we recorded $3.7 million in incremental pre-tax charges in that year related to the", "bbox": [206.3, 1307.4, 1186.8, 1328.1]}, {"text": "termination of the previous credit arrangement.", "bbox": [206.3, 1331.4, 599.8, 1352.2]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [131.3, 1372.2, 138.5, 1392.9]}, {"text": "In 2008 we sold our Vision Events business, which had been part of our Events segment. Accordingly, the results of", "bbox": [206.3, 1372.2, 1186.9, 1392.9]}, {"text": "operations of this business and the related gain on sale were reported as a discontinued operation.", "bbox": [206.3, 1395.9, 1017.4, 1416.7]}]}